Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 133rd Weekly Dose of Optimism. Just a =
deluge of big, optimistic news to process this week: breakthrough research =
reports, splashy $500B investments, major crypto deregulation, and not one,=
 not two, but three lunar lander launches. Good news from every part of the=
